cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with language modeling and evaluation, specifically in the context of Russian language. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of vector space models, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation of models, which could fall under cs.LG (Learning). The use of machine learning techniques for language modeling could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the study of applicability of models to other languages, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
